description: Outsnap CSWP is a lightweight, athletic, 3 season shoe with a slim profile that's great for everyday life in the city or the mountains. It has a microfleece lining and winter insole for added warmth, protective mid-cut upper, and a cuhioned midsole. Contagrip® outsole delivers confident grip on hard or soft, wet or dry surfaces.
